hadiths[88]{hadithnumber,text}:
4366,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs zul-hijja ka chaand dekh ley aur wo qurbani karney ka irada rakhta ho to wo apney baal aur nakhun na kaatey yahan tak ke qurbani kar ley.
4367,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs qurbani karney ka irada rakhta ho, wo na apney nakhun katwaaey aur na baal. ye hukm zul-hijja key pehley das din key liye hai."
4368,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke jo aadmi qurbani zibeh karney ka irada rakhta ho aur zul-hijja shuru ho jaey to wo apney baal aur nakhun na kaatey. mainey Ikrima sey us ka zikr kiya to wo kehney lagey : kya wo aurat aur khushbu sey bhi alag na rahey?
4369,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab zul-hijja shuru ho jaey to jo shakhs qurbani ka irada rakhta ho, to wo apney baal ya jism ka koi aur hissa (maslan nakhun waghera) na kaatey."
4370,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey farmaya : mujhey qurbaaniyon waley din ko eid bananey ka hukm diya gaya hai jisey Allah Taala ney is ummat key liye muqarrar farmaya hai. us shakhs ney arz kiya : agar merey paas doodh wali bakri key ilawa koi aur janwer qurbani key liye na ho to farmaiye kya main usey hi zibeh kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. lekin to (qurbani waley din) apney baal kaat ley, nakhun aur munchhen tarash ley aur zere-naf baal saaf kar ley. Allah Taala key yahan teri taraf sey yehi mukammal qurbani shumar hogi."
4371,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eid-gaah mein qurbani zibeh ya nahar farmatey they.
4372,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Eidul-Azhaa key din Madina Munawra mein oont nahar farmaya. aur agar (kisi saal) oont nahar na farmatey to qurbani ko Eid-gaah mein zibeh farmatey.
4373,"Hazrat Jundub bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eidul-azhaa mein hazir huwa. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko namaz padhaai. jab aap ney namaz ada kar li to aap ney dekha ke kuchh bakriyan zibeh ho chuki hain. aap ney farmaya : jisney namaz sey pehley qurbani zibeh kar di hai, wo uski jagah aur bakri zibeh karey aur jo zibeh nahin kar chuka to wo Allah ka naam ley kar zibeh kerey."
4374,"Hazrat Abu Zahhaak Ubaid bin Feeroz Mola bani Shebaan sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) sey arz kiya : mujhey bataiye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kin janweron ki qurbani sey mana farmaya hai? unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khutba deney key liye uthey aur (apney haath mubarak key sath ishara kartey huye ) farmaya : wesey mera haath har lihaz sey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key haath sey chhota hai. chaar janwer qurbani mein kifaayat nahin kartey : kaanaa janwer jis ka kaanaa pan wazeh ho, bimar janwer jiski bimari wazeh ho, langdaa janwer jis ka langdaa-pan wazeh ho. aur wo janwer jo haddi tootney sey itna kamzor ho chuka ho ke is mein goodaa na raha ho. mainey kaha : main to ye bhi napasand karta hun ke seeng mein koi nuqs ho ya daant mein koi nuqs ho. wo farmaney lagey : jisey to napasand karta hai, uski qurbani na kar lekin kisi par haram na kar."
4375,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Feeroz sey manqul hai ke mainey Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : mujhey bayan farmaiye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kin janweron ki qurbani sey mana farmaya hai ya napasand farmaya hai? wo farmaney lagey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney daste-mubarak sey yun ishara farmaya : … aur mera haath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key haath sey chhota hai … . chaar janwer qurbani mein kifaayat nahin kartey : kaanaa jis ka kaanaa pan wazeh ho, bimar jiski bimari wazeh ho, langdaa jis ka langdaa-pan wazeh ho aur wo janwer jiski haddi toot chuki ho aur wo itna kamzor ho chuka ho ke is mein goodaa baqi na raha ho. mainey kaha : main to kaan aur seeng key nuqs ko bhi napasand karta hun. wo farmaney lagey : jis ko to napasand karta hai usey qurban na kar lekin usey dusron key liye haram qarar na dey."
4376,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aur aap apni mubarak ungliyon key sath ishara bhi farma rahey they : … aur meri ungliyan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki muqaddas ungliyon sey chhoti hain … . chaar qism key janwer qurbani mein jayez nahin : kaanaa jis ka kaanaa pan zahir ho, langdaa jis ka langdaa-pan wazeh ho, mareez jis ka marz wazeh ho aur itna kamzor janwer ke is mein goodaa tak na ho."
4377,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya ke hum (qurbani waley janwer key) aankh aur kaan ko ghor sey dekhen aur hum koi aisa janwer zibeh na karen jis ka kaan aagey sey kataa ho ya peechhey sey kataa huwa ho ya dum kati hui ho ya kaan mein surakh ho.
4378,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya ke hum (qurbani waley janwer key) aankh aur kaan ko achchhi tarah dekhen. aur hum koi aisa janwer zibeh na karen jo kaanaa ho ya us ka kaan aagey ya peechhey sey kataa huwa ho, ya wo darmiyan sey chiraa huwa ho ya is mein surakh ho."
4379,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke aisa janwer qurbani mein zibeh kiya jaey jis ka kaan aagey ya peechhey sey kataa ya chiraa huwa ho ya is mein surakh ho. ya us ka koi uzu kataa huwa ho.
4380,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aisa janwer qurbani mein zibeh na kiya jaey jis ka kaan aagey ya peechhey sey kataa huwa ho ya chiraa huwa ho, ya is mein surakh ho, ya wo aankh sey kaanaa ho."
4381,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya ke hum qurbani key janwer key kaan aur aankh ghor sey dekhen (ke un mein kisi qism ki koi kharabi na ho).
4382,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tootey huye seeng waley janwer ki qurbani sey mana farmaya hai. ye baat Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey zikr ki gaee to unhoney farmaya : is sey murad wo janwer hai jis ka nisf (aadha) ya nisf (aadhe se) ziyada seeng tootaa huwa ho.
4383,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum qurbani mein sirf musinna janwer hi zibeh karo siwaey iske tumhein musanna milna mushkil ho to phir tum bheed ka Juzaa zibeh kar saktey ho.
4384,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey kuchh bakriyan dein ke sahaba mein taqseem kar dey. aakhir main eik Juzaa (bakri ka eik saala bacha, yani memna) bach gaya. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : chalo ! tum iski qurbani kar do."
4385,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba mein qurbani key janwer taqseem farmaey. merey liye eik Juzaa reh gaya. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey liye Juzaa bachcha hai. aap ney farmaya : to wohi qurban kar dey.
4386,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba mein qurbani key janwer taqseem farmaey. mujhey eik Juzaa mila. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey Juzaa mila hai. aap ney farmaya : to yehi zibeh kar dey.
4387,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey sath qurbani mein bheed key juzaa zibeh kiye.
4388,"Hazrat Aasim bin Kulaib key walid mohtaram ney farmaya : hum eik safar mein they. qurbaaniyon ka waqt aa gaya to hum mein sey koi shakhs do do, teen teen juzaa dey kar musanna khareedtaa tha. Muzena qabiley ka eik shakhs hamein kehney laga : hum eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke ye din (eidul-Azhaa) aa gaya to log do do, teen teen juzaa dey kar musanna khareedney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Juzaa kifaayat kar sakta hai jahan do daantaa kifaayat karta hai."
4389,eik sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum eidul-azhaa sey do din qabl (pehley) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. hum do daante key iwaz do-do juzaa detey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do daante ki jagah Juzaa bhi kifaayat kar sakta hai.
4390,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do mendhey qurban kiya kartey they aur main bhi do mendhey hi qurban karta hun.
4391,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney do chitkabrey mendhey qurban kiye.
4392,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney do chitkabrey, seengon waley mendhey qurban kiye. aap ney in ko apney haath sey zibeh farmaya. Bismillah padhi aur Allahu-Akbar kaha aur apna paaun un ki gardan key pehlu par rakha."
4393,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eidul-azhaa key din khutba irshad farmaya, phir do siyah aur safed mendhon ki taraf badhey aur in ko zibeh farmaya. (ye riwayat) mukhtasar hai."
4394,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke phir Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qurbani waley din do siyah aur safed mendhon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur unhein zibeh farmaya, isi ke sath aap ney kuchh bakriyan sahaba mein taqseem farmaeen (taake wo bhi qurbani kar saken)."
4395,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik nar, seengon wala mendhaa qurban farmaya jiski taangen siyah thin, munh aur pet bhi siyah tha aur aankhen bhi siyah thin (baqi safed tha)."
4396,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghanimat taqseem farmatey waqt das bakriyon ko eik oont key barabar rakha kartey they. (raawi hadees Imam) Shoba ney ye hadees (حدثنا سفیان الثوری ، عن ابیہ) ki sanad sey bayan ki hai, yani Shoba ye hadees Sufiyan Sauri sey aur wo apney baap (Saeed bin Masruq) sey bayan kartey hain, taaham Imam Shoba farmatey hain ke mera khayal hai ke main ye hadees (Sufiyan Sauri key wastey key baghair) us (Sufiyan) key walid mohtaram Saeed bin Masruq sey bhi suni hai."
4397,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. qurbaaniyon ka waqt aa gaya to hum oont mein das aur gaaey mein saat afrad shareek huye.
4398,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tamatto kiya to hum gaaey saat afrad ki taraf sey zibeh kartey they aur is mein shareek hotey they.
4399,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Eidul-Azhaa key din (khutba irshad farmaney key liye) khadey huye aur farmaya : jo shakhs hamarey qibley ki taraf munh karta hai, hamari tarah namaz padhta hai aur hamari tarah qurbani karta hai to wo apni qurbani zibeh na karey yahan tak ke namaz, eid ki namaz padh ley. merey mamu khadey huye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey to apni qurbani jaldi zibeh kar li taake main apney ghar walon aur mohalley-daar padausiyon ko (jaldi) gosht khilaaun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aur qurbani zibeh kar. unhoney kaha : merey paas bakri ka eik maada bachcha hai jo mujhey gosht key lihaz sey do bakriyon sey bhi achchhaa lagta hai. aap ney farmaya : usey hi zibeh kar dey. wo teri do qurbaaniyon mein sey achchhi qurbani hogi. lekin terey ilawa kisi ki taraf sey Juzaa qurbani mein kifaayat nahin karega."
4400,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbani waley din eid ki namaz key baad hamein khutba irshad farmaya : jo shakhs hum jaisi namaz padhta hai aur hum jaisi qurbani karta hai, us ney to sahih qurbani ki aur jisney namaz padhney sey pehley hi qurbani kar di to wo gosht wali bakri hai (woh sirf gosht key liye zibeh kiya gaya janwer mutsawwir hoga. qurbani nahin hogi). Hazrat Abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! mainey to namaz key liye aaney sey pehley qurbani zibeh kar di thi. mainey samjha ke ye sara din hi khaney peeney key liye hai, is liye mainey jald bazi ki. khud bhi gosht khaya aur ghar walon aur padausiyon ko bhi khilaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to gosht wali bakri ho gaee (qurbani nahin hui). unhoney arz kiya : merey paas eik Juzaa bakri hai jo gosht key lihaz sey do bakriyon sey bhi behtar hai to kya wo mujh sey kifaayat kar jaeygi? aap ney farmaya : haan. lekin wo terey ilawa kisi aur sey kifaayat nahin keregi."
4401,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbaaniyon key din farmaya : jis shakhs ney eid ki namaz sey pehley qurbani zibeh kar li hai wo dobara zibeh kerey. eik aadmi uth kar kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye din aisa hai ke is mein gosht ki khahish hoti hai, phir us ney apney padausiyon ki mushkil haalat (mohtaji aur faqr (gharibi) aur faaqey) ka zikr kiya. aisey lagta tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi uski tasdeeq farma rahey hain. us ney kaha : merey paas eik Juzaa (bakri ka chhoti umr ka bachcha) hai jo gosht ki do bakriyon sey bhi mujhey ziyada pasand hai. aap ney usey wohi Juzaa zibeh karney ki rukhsat (chhoot) di. main nahin janta ke ye rukhsat (chhoot) uskey ilawa dusrey logon ko bhi pahunchi ya nahin, phir aap do mendhon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur unhein zibeh kiya."
4402,Hazrat Abu-Barda bin Niyar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney apni qurbani Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey pehley zibeh kar di thi to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein dobara qurbani karney ka hukm diya. unhoney kaha : merey paas eik Juzaa bakri hai jo merey nazdik (gosht key lihaz sey) do musannon sey bhi behtar hai. iskey ilawa aur koi nahin. aap ney farmaya : usey zibeh kar do.
4403,"Hazrat Jundub bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath qurbaaniyaan zibeh kein to dekha ke kuchh log namaz sey pehley hi apni qurbaaniyaan zibeh kar chukey they. jab aap farigh huye to aap ko pata chala ke wo namaz sey pehley hi zibeh kar chukey hain to aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney qurbani namaz sey pehley zibeh ki hai, wo uski jagah aur qurbani zibeh karey aur jis shakhs ney namaz sey pehley zibeh nahin ki, wo ab Allah ka naam ley kar zibeh kerey."
4404,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney do khargosh pakdey lekin in ko zibeh karney key liye unhein koi chhuri waghera na mili to unhoney in ko eik tez dhaar patthar sey zibeh kar diya, phir wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey do khargosh shikar kiye they lekin mujhey koi chhuri waghera nahin mili jis sey zibeh karta. to mainey eik tez dhaar patthar sey in ko zibeh kar diya. kya main in ko kha sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : haan, kha ley."
4405,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik bhediye ney eik bakri mein daant gaad diye. logon ney (us ko chhudaney key baad) usey eik tez dhaar patthar sey zibeh kar diya. to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey khaney ki ijazat di.
4406,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apna kutta chhodta hun aur shikar ko pakad leta hun lekin mujhey koi aisi chiz nahin milti jis sey zibeh kar sakun to kya main usey tez dhaar patthar ya lakdi sey zibeh kar sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : jis chiz sey bhi ho sakey, khoon baha dey, albatta Allah ka naam zarur ley."
4407,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi ke eik Ansari ki oontni uhad ki taraf char rahi thi ke wo qaribul-maut ho gaee. us Ansari ney usey eik nauk daar khuntey key sath nahar (zibeh) kar diya. (raawi hadees Ayub ya Jareer ney kaha) mainey puchha ke wo khunta lakdi ka tha ya lohey ka? ustaad ney kaha : nahin, wo lakdi ka tha, phir wo Ansari Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap sey masla puchha. aap ney usey khaney ka hukm diya."
4408,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo chiz khoon baha dey aur Allah ka naam liya gaya ho to ( wo zabiha ) kha ley magar daant aur nakhun ka zibeh nahin.
4409,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kal dushman sey milengey (aur wahan janwer bhi bator ghanimat milengey) aur hamarey paas chhuriyaan waghera na hon to (hum janwer kaisey zibeh keren)? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo chiz bhi khoon baha dey aur Allah Taala ka naam liya jaey to ( zabiha halal hai) kha saktey ho ba-sharte-ke wo chiz nakhun ya daant na ho. aur main tumhein iski wajeh bhi bayan karta hun ke daant to eik haddi hai aur nakhun habshiyon ki chhuri hai.
4410,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke do baaten mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey khub yad rakhi hain. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney zaroori qarar diya hai ke har chiz par ehsan kiya jaey, lihaza jab tum (kisi insan ko qisaas mein ya kisi moozi janwer aur darindey waghera ko) qatl karney lago to achchhey tareeqey sey qatl karo. aur jab tum zibeh karney lago (kisi perindey ya halal janwer ko) to achchhey tareeqey sey zibeh karo. aur zibeh kartey waqt chhuri tez kar liya karo aur apney zabiha ko aaram pahunchao."
4411,"Hazrat Asma bint Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein ghodaa nahar kiya, phir usey khaya."
4412,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik bhediye ney eik bakri mein daant gaad diye. logon ney (us sey chuda kar) us ko eik tez dhaar patthar sey zibeh kar diya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko khaney ki ijazat dey di.
4413,Hazrat Abu Ushraa key walid mohtaram bayan kartey hain ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya zibeh sirf halaq aur seeney key gadhey hi mein ho sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : agar to uskey raan mein neza ya barchhi waghera maar dey to bhi kifaayat kar jaaeyga.
4414,"Hazrat Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kal hamara dushman sey muqabla hoga. hamarey paas chhuri qisam ki chiz nahin (to zibeh kaisey keren?) aap ney farmaya : jo chiz bhi khoon baha dey aur Allah Taala ka naam zikr kar diya jaey to ( aisa zabiha ) khaya ja sakta hai. ilawa daant aur nakhun key. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ghanimat mein oont hasil huye. un mein sey eik oont bhag gaya. eik aadmi ney us ko (peechhey sey) teer maara jis sey wo ruk gaya. aap ney farmaya : ye gharelu janwer ya oont bhi kabhi jangli janweron ki tarah be-qabu ho jatey hain, lihaza jo janwer tum sey be-qabu ho jaey, us sey yehi sulook karo."
4415,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kal dushman sey hamari mulaqat hogi aur hamarey paas chhuri (waghera kuchh) nahin. aap ney farmaya : jo chiz bhi khoon baha dey ba-sharte-ke Allah ka naam liya gaya ho, usey kha saktey ho. ilawa daant aur nakhun key. aur uski wajeh bhi main tumhen bayan karta hun : daant to haddi hai aur nakhun habshiyon ki chhuri hai. hamein is jang mein oont aur bakriyan maale-ghanimat mein hasil huin. un mein sey eik oont bhag gaya to eik aadmi ney teer maar kar usey rok diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye oont bhi kabhi jangli janweron ki tarah bhag uthtey hain. jab wo tum sey be-qabu ho jaeyn to tum un sey yehi sulook karo."
4416,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah Taala ney har chiz key sath hussne-sulook farz qarar diya hai, lihaza jab tum kisi ko (qisaas waghera mein) qatl karney lago to achchhey tareeqey sey qatl karo aur jab tum kisi janwer ko zibeh karney lago to achchhey tareeqey sey zibeh karo. aur zibeh kartey waqt apni chhuri ko tez karo aur apney zabiha ko jaldi najat do."
4417,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har chiz sey hussne-sulook karna Allah Taala ney farz qarar diya hai, is liye jab tum kisi ko qatl karney lago to achchhey tareeqey sey qatl karo aur jab tum kisi janwer ko zibeh karney lago to achchhey tareeqey sey zibeh karo. zibeh karney wala shakhs apni chhuri ko tez karey aur apney zibeh kiye jane wale janwer ko rahat pahunchaey."
4418,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey do baaten sunen. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney har chiz sey hussne-sulook zaroori qarar diya hai, lihaza jab tum kisi ko qatl karo to achchhey tareeqey sey karo aur jab kisi janwer ko zibeh karo to achchhey tareeqey sey zibeh karo. zibeh karney wala shakhs apni chhuri ko tez karey aur apney zabiha ko aaram pahunchaey."
4419,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke do baaten mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey yad rakhin : (aap ney farmaya : ) yaqinan Allah Taala ney har chiz sey hussne-sulook zaroori qarar diya hai, lihaza jab tum kisi ko qatl karney lago to achchhey tareeqey sey qatl karo aur jab tum kisi janwer ko zibeh karney lago to achchhey tareeqey sey zibeh karo. zibeh karney wala apni chhuri ko tez kar ley aur apney zibeh honey waley janwer ko kam sey kam takleef pahunchaey. (matlab ye ke yakbaargi zibeh kerey, der na lagaey.)"
4420,"Hazrat Qatada (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney do chitkabrey (siyah aur safed), seengon waley mendhey qurbani farmaee. zibeh farmatey waqt aap بسم اللہ و اللہ اکبر they. mainey aap ko apney daste-mubarak sey unhen zibeh farmatey dekha jabkey aap ney apna qadam mubarak unkey pehlu par rakha huwa tha. (Shoba ney kaha) mainey (Qatada sey) kaha : kya aap ney un (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) sey suna? unhoney farmaya : haan."
4421,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do siyah aur safed, seengon waley mendhey zibeh kartey they. aap بسم اللہ و اللہ اکبر padhtey they. mainey aap ko apney daste-mubarak sey unhen zibeh kartey dekha. aap ney apna paon mubarak unkey pehlu par rakha huwa tha."
4422,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap do siyah aur safed, seengon waley mendhon ko بسم اللہ و اللہ اکبر padhtey huye apney daste-mubarak sey zibeh farma rahey they aur apna qadam mubarak unkey pehlu par rakha huwa tha."
4423,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney seengon waley siyah aur safed do mendhey بسم اللہ و اللہ اکبر padhtey huye qurban farmaai jabkey aap ney unkey pehlu par paon mubarak rakha huwa tha.
4424,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni qurbani key kuchh oont khud nahar farmaai aur kuchh oont kisi aur ney nahar kiye.
4425,Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein ghodaa nahar kiya aur phir us ka gosht khaya. Quteba (ustaad) ney kaha : (فَأَکَلْنَا لَحْمَہٗ) phir hamney us ka gosht khaya. Abda bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney iski mukhalifat ki hai.
4426,Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mubarak mein Madina mein rehtey huye ghodaa zibeh (nahar) kiya aur phir usey khaya.
4427,"Hazrat Aamir bin Waasla sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aap ko logon sey alag koi poshida baaten batlaya kartey they? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ghazab naak ho gaey yahan tak ke unka chehra surkh ho gaya. aur aap ney farmaya : aap mujhey logon sey alag koi poshida baat nahin batlaatey they, albatta eik dafa aap ney mujhey ye chaar baaten irshad farmaen jabkey us waqt ghar mein, main aur aap hi they. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs par lanat karey jo apney baap ko lanat karta hai. Allah Taala us shakhs par lanat karey jo ghairullah key liye zibeh karta hai. Allah Taala us shakhs par lanat karey jo kisi bid'ati ya baaghi ko thikana mohaiyya karta hai aur Allah Taala us shakhs par bhi lanat karey jo zamin ki alaamaat ko tabdeel karta hai."
4428,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen din sey zayed qurbaaniyon ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya.
4429,"Hazrat Abu-Ubaid sey riwayat hai ke mainey eid key din Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) key sath eid padhi. aap ney khutbey sey pehley namaze-eid padhaai. Azan hui na iqaamat, phir farmaney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht rakhney sey mana farmatey they."
4430,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen teen din sey zayed apni qurbaaniyon key gosht khaney sey mana farma diya hai.
4431,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya tha, phir aap ney farmaya : ab khao. safar mein bhi sath ley jao aur zakhira bhi karo."
4432,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Khubab sey riwayat hai ke Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) eik safar sey wapis tashrif laye to unkey ghar walon ney in ko qurbani ka gosht pesh kiya. wo farmaney lagey : main to nahin khaaunga yahan tak ke main ye masla poochhun, phir wo apney Akhyafi (maa sharik) (maadri) bhai Hazrat Qatada bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) jo Badri sahabi they, key paas gaey aur un sey iskey mutalliq puchha to unhoney bataya : aap key baad eik naya hukm jari ho chuka hai, us hukm ko khatam karney key liye jis mein unhen (sahaba kiram ko) teen din key baad qurbaaniyon ka gosht khaney sey mana kar diya gaya tha. (matlab ye hai ke tumharey baad eik naya hukm jari ho chuka hai. jis sey teen din key baad qurbani ka gosht na khaney ka hukm mansookh ho gaya hai.)"
4433,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya hai. Hazrat Qatada bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) aaye jo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) key Akhyafi (maa sharik) (maadri) bhai aur Badri sahabi they. ghar walon ney unhen gosht pesh kiya to wo farmaney lagey : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is sey mana nahin farmaya? Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri ney farmaya : iski baabat naya farman jari ho chuka hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pehley teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya tha, phir ijazat farma di ke hum kha bhi saktey hain aur zakhira bhi kar saktey hain."
4434,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhen teen baaton sey roka tha : (eik to mainey tumhen) qabron par janey sey (roka tha). ab jaya karo lekin qabron par jana tumhari neki mein izaafey ka zariya ban'na chahiye. (doosra) mainey tumhen teen din sey zayed qurbaaniyon ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya tha, ab khao jab tak chaho. aur rakho jab tak chaho. aur (teesra) mainey tumhen chand bartanon mein (pani ya nabeez) peeney sey roka tha, ab tum jis bartan mein chaho pi saktey ho lekin koi nashey wali chiz na peena. Muhammad (ibne Ma'daan) ney (وَ اَمْسِکُوْا) key alfaz bayan kiye. (matlab ye ke ye alfaz ustaad Amr bin Mansoor ney bayan kiye hain.)"
4435,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhen teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht khaney sey roka tha, aur mishkeezey key ilawa kisi bartan mein nabeez bananey sey bhi roka tha. isi tarah qabron par janey sey bhi mana kiya tha. ab tum jab tak chaho, qurbani ka gosht kha saktey ho. safar mein sath bhi ley ja saktey ho aur zakhira bhi kar saktey ho. aur jo shakhs chahey, qabron par ja sakta hai kyonkey wo aakhirat yad dilati hain. isi tarah ab tum har bartan mein nabeez bana kar pi saktey ho lekin har nashey wali chiz sey bacho."
4436,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke dehatiyon ka eik qafila Madina Munawra aaya. udhar qurbaaniyon ka waqt aa gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qurbaaniyon ka gosht) teen din rakh kar kha saktey ho (zayed nahin). iskey baad (aainda saal) logon key arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! log apni qurbaaniyon sey faeyda uthaya kartey they. un ki charbi pighla liya kartey they aur chamdon sey mishkeezey bana liya kartey they. aap ney farmaya : kya matlab? logon ney kaha : aap ney jo qurbani ka gosht waghera rakhney sey rok diya hai. aap ney farmaya : mainey to us qafley ki wajeh sey roka tha jo (dehat sey) aaya tha. ab tum khao, jama bhi rakho aur sadqa bhi karo."
4437,"Hazrat Aabis sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key yahan hazir huwa aur puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qurbani ka gosht teen din sey zayed khaney sey roktey they? unhoney farmaya : han, log bahut tang they, is liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney behtar samjha ke maal-daar log faqiron ko khilaeyn, phir farmaney lagen : mainey dekha hai ke aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) pandarah pandarah din key baad qurbani key janweron key paey khatey they. mainey kaha : aisey kyon? hans kar farmaney lagen : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghar walon ney teen din musalsal salan wali roti sair ho kar nahin khai. yahan tak ke aap Allah key paas tashrif ley gaey."
4438,Hazrat Aabis ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey qurbani key gosht key barey mein puchha. unhoney farmaya : hum eik eik maah tak qurbani key paaey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye rakh chhodtey they. aur aap kha liya kartey they.
4439,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pehley teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht rakhney sey mana farma diya tha, phir aap ney farmaya : (jab tak chaho) khao aur (fuqaraa aur miskinon ko bhi) khilao."
4440,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke khaibar key din charbi ka eik thailaa (qil'a sey) bahar phenka gaya. main us sey chimat gaya. mainey (apney aap sey) kaha : main is sey kisi ko kuchh nahin dunga. achcha main muda to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (mujhey dekh sun kar) muskura rahey they.
4441,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke kuchh erabi (dehati) log hamarey paas gosht latey they aur hamein malum nahin hota tha unhoney (zibeh kartey waqt) Allah Taala ka naam liya hai ya nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum Allah Taala ka naam ley kar kha liya karo.
4442,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Allah Taala key farman : (وَ لَا تَاْکُلُوْا مِمَّا لَمْ یُذْکَرِاسْمُ اللّٰہِ عَلَیْہِ),''woh janwer na khao jis par Allah ka naam na liya gaya ho.'' key barey mein farmaya : mushrekin ney musalmanon sey hujjat bazi ki thi ke jis janwer ko Allah Taala zibeh kerey. usey tum nahin khatey aur jisey tum khud zibeh kartey ho, usey kha letey ho?"
4443,Hazrat Abu Sa'alba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujassma halal nahin.
4444,Hazrat Hisham bin Zaid sey manqul hai ke main Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Hukm bin Ayub key paas gaya to kuchh log Ameer key ghar main eik murghi ko nishana bana kar teer maar rahey they. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya hai ke janweron ko baandh kar nishana banaya jaey.
4445,Hazrat Abdullah bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kuchh logon key paas sey guzrey jo eik mendhey ko nishana bana kar teer maar rahey they. aap ney us ko sakht napasand kiya aur farmaya : janweron ka musla na karo.
4446,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us shakhs par lanat farmaee hai jo kisi jandaar ko nishana banaey.
4447,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah Taala us shakhs par lanat farmaai jo kisi jandaar ka musla kerey.
4448,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aisi chiz jis mein rooh ho usey nishana na banao.
4449,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi jandaar chiz ko nishana bananey sey mana farmaya hai.
4450,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooan (sidhey taur par) riwayat hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney chidiyaa ya us sey badey kisi janwer ko nahaq qatl kiya, Allah Taala qiyamat key din us sey uskey mutalliq puchheyga. puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! us ka haq kya hai? aap ney farmaya is ka haq ye hai ke usey zibeh kar key khaye. us ka sar kaat kar phenk na dey."
4451,"Hazrat Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jis shakhs ney eik chidiyaa ko bhi be faeyda qatl kiya, qiyamat key din chidiyaa us shakhs key khilaf baa-aawaze-buland Allah Taala sey fariyad kartey huye kahegi : aey merey Parwardigar ! falan shakhs ney mujhey be-faeyda qatl kiya. kisi faaedey key liye zibeh nahin kiya."
4452,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar (ki jang) key din gharelu (paaltu) gadhon key gosht sey, isi ke sath gandagi khaney waley janweron key gosht aur sawari sey mana farmaya tha."
4453,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujassama, gandagi khaney waley janwer key doodh aur mishkeezey key munh sey (us key munh sey, munh laga kar) pani peeney sey mana farmaya hai."
